Installation

Create directory:

    mkdir ~/bin/
    cd ~/bin/

Clone repository:

    git clone git://github.com/mikero/dotfiles.git

Symlink to .vimrc, .vim, .bashrc, and .gitconfig:

    ln -nfs ~/bin/dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -nfs ~/bin/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -nfs ~/bin/dotfiles/bashrc ~/.bashrc
    ln -nfs ~/bin/dotfiles/gitconfig ~/.gitconfig

